OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy and dull day with rain
OL,6,Fand drizzle across the Central Belt
OL,7,Fand Argyll, rain becoming lighter and
OL,8,Fpatchier in the afternoon. Drier
OL,9,Ffurther south across Ayrshire but
OL,10,Fstill cloudy with some outbreaks of
OL,11,Frain possible. Windy.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FIt will be cloudy and
OL,14,Fovercast through the evening and
OL,15,Fovernight with outbreaks of light and
OL,16,Fpatchy rain for all areas but
OL,17,Fespecially Argyll. Winds falling light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
