OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FAnother cloudy and dull day
OL,6,Fwith outbreaks of rain and drizzle
OL,7,Fthroughout, which may be heavy and
OL,8,Fpersistent at times, particularly over
OL,9,FArgyll. Breezy.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FCloudy
OL,12,Fand breezy on Monday and Tuesday with
OL,13,Foutbreaks of rain spreading east,
OL,14,Fperhaps becoming heavy and persistent
OL,15,Fat times. Drier with brighter spells
OL,16,Fon Wednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
